l2 style=''margin-bottom:0cm''><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:  8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif;color:black''>16.5<span style=''font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"''>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif''>Yolt  is located at 8-10 Moorgate, London EC2R 6DA, United Kingdom.</span></p>    <p class=Level2 style=''margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm''><span lang=EN-GB  style=''font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif''>&nbsp;</span></p>    <p class=Level1 style=''margin-bottom:0cm''><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:  8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif;color:black''>17.<span style=''font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"''>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span><b><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif''>OTHER  IMPORTANT TERMS</span></b></p>    <p class=Level2 style=''margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;  margin-left:42.5pt;text-indent:-42.5pt''><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:8.0pt;  font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif;color:black''>17.1<span style=''font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"''>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif''>Yolt  may transfer our rights and obligations under these Yolt Terms to another  organisation (within the Yolt Group organised under Yolt Group BV but also  third parties), but this will not reduce your rights or those obligations.  You  may not transfer your rights or obligations under these Yolt Terms to another  person.</span></p>    <p class=Level2 style=''margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;  margin-left:42.5pt;text-indent:-42.5pt''><span lang=EN-GB style=''font-size:8.0pt;  font-family:"Verdana",sans-serif;color:black''>17.2<span style=''font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"''>&nbsp;&nb